e » :", "words": [78, 79, 80, 81, 82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 89, 90, 91, 92, 93, 94, 95, 96, 97, 98, 99, 100, 101, 102, 103]}, {"id": 13, "text": "François est gran.", "words": [104, 105, 106]}, {"id": 14, "text": "blond et Françoise est grande, blonde et intelligente.", "words": [107, 108, 109, 110, 111, 112, 113, 114]}, {"id": 15, "text": "M Parfois, on double la consonne finale au féminin :", "words": [115, 116, 117, 118, 119, 120, 121, 122, 123, 124]}, {"id": 16, "text": "Giorgio est italien.", "words": [125, 126, 127]}, {"id": 17, "text": "Bruna est italienne.", "words": [128, 129, 130]}, {"id": 18, "text": "-en/-enne Ilest mignon.", "words": [131, 132, 133]}, {"id": 19, "text": "Elle est mignonne.", "words": [134, 135, 136]}, {"id": 20, "text": "-on/-onne Îl'est ponctuel.", "words": [137, 138, 139]}, {"id": 21, "text": "Elle est ponctuelle.", "words": [140, 141, 142]}, {"id": 22, "text": "-el/-elle", "words": [143]}, {"id": 23, "text": "M Parfois, toute la finale change au féminin :", "words": [144, 145, 146, 147, 148, 149, 150, 151, 152]}, {"id": 24, "text": "Marc est sportif.", "words": [153, 154, 155]}, {"id": 25, "text": "Cathy est sportive.", "words": [156, 157, 158]}, {"id": 26, "text": "/ve", "words": [159]}, {"id": 27, "text": "Il est sérieux.", "words": [160, 161, 162]}, {"id": 28, "text": "Elle est sérieuse.", "words": [163, 164, 165]}, {"id": 29, "text": "-eux/-euse", "words": [166]}, {"id": 30, "text": "Îl est rêveur.", "words": [167, 168, 169]}, {"id": 31, "text": "Elle est -eur/-euse", "words": [170, 171, 172]}, {"id": 32, "text": "Il est calculateur.", "words": [173, 174, 175]}, {"id": 33, "text": "Elle est calculatrice.", "words": [176, 177, 178]}, {"id": 34, "text": "-teur/-trice Il'est étranger.", "words": [179, 180, 181]}, {"id": 35, "text": "Elle est étrangère.", "words": [182, 183, 184]}, {"id": 36, "text": "-er/-ère", "words": [185]}, {"id": 37, "text": "Il est discret.", "words": [186, 187, 188]}, {"id": 38, "text": "Elle est discrète.", "words": [189, 190, 191]}, {"id": 39, "text": "et/-ète", "words": [192]}, {"id": 40, "text": "M Cas particuliers :", "words": [193, 194, 195, 196]}, {"id": 41, "text": "beau/belle nouveau/nouvelle faux/fausse doux/douce roux/rousse jaloux/jalouse gentil/gentille vieux/vieille gros/grosse bas/basse fou/folle long/longue frais/fraîche sec/sèche blanc/blanche grec/grecque public/publique", "words": [197, 198, 199, 200, 201, 202, 203, 204, 205, 206, 207, 208, 209, 210, 211, 212, 213]}, {"id": 42, "text": "Adjectifs de couleur, p.", "words": [214, 215, 216, 217]}, {"id": 43, "text": "14 Professions, p.", "words": [218, 219, 220]}, {"id": 44, "text": "34 Place des adjectifs, p.", "words": [221, 222, 223, 224, 225]}, {"id": 45, "text": "54", "words": [226]}, {"id": 46, "text": "12 e douze", "words": [227, 228, 229]}]}